Admin --> UC38
Admin --> UC39
Admin --> UC40

' Triage Specialist Relationships
Triage --> UC11
Triage --> UC12
Triage --> UC13
Triage --> UC14
Triage --> UC15
Triage --> UC16
Triage --> UC17
Triage --> UC18
Triage --> UC19
Triage --> UC36
Triage --> UC37
Triage --> UC38
Triage --> UC39
Triage --> UC40

' Financial Officer Relationships
Finance --> UC20
Finance --> UC21
Finance --> UC22
Finance --> UC23
Finance --> UC24
Finance --> UC25
Finance --> UC26
Finance --> UC27
Finance --> UC28
Finance --> UC36
Finance --> UC37
Finance --> UC38
Finance --> UC39
Finance --> UC40

' Support Staff Relationships
Support --> UC29
Support --> UC30
Support --> UC31
Support --> UC32
Support --> UC33
Support --> UC34
Support --> UC35
Support --> UC36
Support --> UC37
Support --> UC38
Support --> UC40

' Include relationships
UC1 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
UC12 ..> UC13 : <<include>>
UC21 ..> UC20 : <<include>>
UC23 ..> UC21 : <<include>>
UC30 ..> UC29 : <<include>>

' Extend relationships
UC3 ..> UC2 : <<extend>>
UC6 ..> UC2 : <<extend>>
UC14 ..> UC12 : <<extend>>
UC18 ..> UC12 : <<extend>>
UC22 ..> UC20 : <<extend>>
UC27 ..> UC20 : <<extend>>
UC34 ..> UC30 : <<extend>>

note right of Admin
  Super Admin can perform
  all administrative tasks
  including staff provisioning
end note

note right of Triage
  Validates and triages
  vulnerability reports
  before org review
end note

note right of Finance
  Manages all financial
  operations and KYC
  verification
end note

note right of Support
  Provides user support
  and platform assistance
end note

@enduml
